Class PowerofTwo<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.uwm.cs351.PowerofTwo<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the vertex ID
All Implemented Interfaces:
Neighborhood<T>
public class PowerofTwo<T> extends Object implements Neighborhood<T>
PowerOfTwoVector is an implementation of the Neighborhood interface, optimized for handling small neighborhoods by using power-of-two-sized vectors. This structure is sorted for efficient intersection operations and neighborhood scans.
